{
  "total_duration": 563.882,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 14.64,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象一个很现实的 city problem：你家车库门口总被别人停车，车子挡住 entrance，你自己的车反而开不进去。你贴了"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No Parking"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，可是别人还是停在那里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 14.99,
      "end": 32.55,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No parking"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“禁止停车”。这课不是单纯讲交通标志，也不是讲 revenge，而是一个城市生活幽默故事：正常规则没用，Jasper 就搬出了一个古代神话里的帮手。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 32.899,
      "end": 49.091,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先把房子结构说清楚。Jasper 有一所 city house，外面有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "gate"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，门后是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "garage"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也就是放车的车库。如果别人把车停在 gate 外面，他就不能把自己的车开进 garage。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 49.441,
      "end": 64.041,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个场景可以想成小区车库入口、地下车库坡道、学校门口、消防通道，或者你家的 private parking space 被占了。问题不是 Jasper 讨厌车，而是入口被堵住了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 64.391,
      "end": 80.654,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里还有一个 myth joke。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Medusa"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "叫“美杜莎”，是 Greek myth 里有名的 Gorgon，常被画成蛇发女怪。传说中，看见她的人可能会"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "turn to stone"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，变成石头。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 81.004,
      "end": 95.404,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以 Jasper 的办法很夸张：如果"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No Parking"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "signs 没有效果，那就把美杜莎石头像放在大门上，希望乱停车的人和车都变成石头。听起来很怪，也正是笑点。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 95.754,
      "end": 108.786,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事开头说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Jasper White is one of those rare people who believes in ancient myths."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "rare"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是少见的，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ancient myths"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是很古老的神话故事。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 109.136,
      "end": 121.435,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他刚在城里买了一所新房子："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He has just bought a new house in the city."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是新家马上带来一个麻烦：他有 gate，有 garage，却常常被外面的车挡住入口。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 121.785,
      "end": 134.769,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Ever since he moved in, he has had trouble with cars and their owners."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ever since"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是从那时起一直到现在。这个 parking trouble 不是一次，是一直发生。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 135.119,
      "end": 149.343,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "晚上他回家时，经常发现"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "someone has parked a car outside his gate"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。因为这样，他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "has not been able to get his own car into his garage even once"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，甚至一次也没成功。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 149.692,
      "end": 160.78,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Jasper 先用了正常办法："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Jasper has put up 'No Parking' signs outside his gate."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "put up"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是挂起、立起，让别人看见。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 161.13,
      "end": 173.266,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "these have not had any effect"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。标志没有效果，车还是堵在 gate 外面。于是他把一个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ugly stone head"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "放到了大门上方。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 173.616,
      "end": 184.024,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "narrator 问他那是什么。Jasper 说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It was Medusa, the Gorgon."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "也就是美杜莎，这个 Greek myth 里的蛇发女怪。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 184.373,
      "end": 197.581,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Jasper 希望她能"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "turn cars and their owners to stone"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。可是结尾很幽默："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "But none of them has been turned to stone yet!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到现在，没有一个真的变成石头。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 197.931,
      "end": 199.451,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课为什么好笑？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 199.801,
      "end": 203.664,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为 Jasper 用神话怪物来解决停车问题？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 204.014,
      "end": 215.534,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。问题本身很 everyday：车堵住 gate，他进不了 garage。正常的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No Parking"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "signs 应该能提醒别人，可是没有效果。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 215.884,
      "end": 220.261,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Medusa"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是恐怖故事吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 220.611,
      "end": 238.21,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这课里不是。我们只要知道 Medusa，美杜莎，是 Greek myth 里的 Gorgon，传说能让人"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "turn to stone"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。很多现代故事和电影也借用过她，比如"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Percy Jackson"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，但今天不用展开讲神话课。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 238.56,
      "end": 241.428,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那现实里可以这样解决吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 241.778,
      "end": 256.338,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不可以。现实里应该 calm and legal：找 property manager，联系车主，或者用清楚合法的 barrier 和 sign。Jasper 的 Medusa 是夸张笑话：modern parking problem meets ancient myth."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 256.688,
      "end": 265.008,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以记住这个 contrast：the signs have not had any effect, and Medusa has not had any effect either. 这就是 punchline。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 265.357,
      "end": 269.821,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Jasper White is one of those rare people who believes in ancient myths."
        }
      ]
    },
