        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "myth"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是神话，通常是很古老的 stories about gods, heroes, monsters, or magic。课文里说 Jasper believes in"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ancient myths"
        },
