      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "These have not had any effect."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这些标志没有任何效果。最后你会发现，Medusa 暂时也没有任何效果。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 407.629,
      "end": 417.349,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 是 present perfect：过去发生的事，到现在仍然有结果。Jasper 的问题不是 yesterday only，而是还在继续。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 417.699,
      "end": 427.899,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "has just bought"
