          "text": "none of them has been turned to stone yet"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。重点不是谁施了魔法，而是 cars and owners 到现在还没有“被变成石头”。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "yet"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是 up to now。"
